-- 047_controller_flash_message_translations.sql
-- Translates every user-facing flash message set via flash_set() across all
-- 17 controllers (235 calls total: 137 plain-literal, 74 with concatenated
-- variables now wired via sprintf()-style t() templates with %s
-- placeholders, plus a handful of shared sub-strings like the
-- "(no location)" suffix reused by multiple controllers). These messages
-- were invisible to the original view-wiring pass (server-side PHP strings,
-- not view markup). Idempotent (ON DUPLICATE KEY UPDATE).

